# Step 10: Check the confirmation-dialog ID

Your update currently contains:

```xhtml
:editCloseFollowUpConfirmDialog
```

This is correct only when the dialog is outside the form:

```xhtml
<h:form id="viewEditContactHistoryForm">
    ...
</h:form>

<p:confirmDialog id="editCloseFollowUpConfirmDialog">
    ...
</p:confirmDialog>
```

When the dialog is inside the form:

```xhtml
<h:form id="viewEditContactHistoryForm">

    <p:confirmDialog id="editCloseFollowUpConfirmDialog">
        ...
    </p:confirmDialog>

</h:form>
```

change the update target to:

```xhtml
:viewEditContactHistoryForm:editCloseFollowUpConfirmDialog
```

