```

## When the image appears

Your resource path and CSS are correct. Replace the test component with the complete Ajax component.

## When the image still does not appear

Open this URL directly in the browser:

```text
http://localhost:9091/midofficetools-webapp/resources/images/common/button-previous.png
```

Possible results:

### Image opens

The image exists. The problem is CSS or positioning.

### HTTP 404

The file location or filename is wrong.

Check exact capitalization:

```text
button-previous.png
button-Previous.png
Button-previous.png
```

These can behave differently when deployed to Linux.

